We are a Verizon Wireless Premium Retailer located in Bayside/Whitestone NY. We are looking for a Retail Sales Associate/Manager to start work immediately.  This is the perfect opportunity for someone who has 1-2 Years of sales experience and is ready to grow in the Wireless industry.   <br>
<br>
Requirements:<br>
<br>
-Must have at least 1 Year of Retail Sales Experience (Preferably Wireless Sales)<br>
-Must be available to work mornings, evenings and weekends<br>
-Must have an outgoing, energetic personality, not afraid to start a conversation<br>
-Must be self-motivated to learn, grow and succeed<br>
-Must enjoy working with customers and providing excellent customer service<br>
-Must be able to multitask, prioritize and problem solve in a fast paced work environment<br>
-Must be proficient in Microsoft Word, Excel & Powerpoint<br>
-Must have an intermediate understanding of Smartphone's and wireless technologies with the ability to expand on that knowledge<br>
<br>
Responsibilities:<br>
<br>
-Greet customers, engage them in relevant conversation to determine their wants and needs and recommend the appropriate devices and accessories to meet those needs<br>
 <br>
-Stay apprised of all current Verizon Wireless promotions and price plans to clearly explain and share with customers<br>
<br>
-Making 2-Day and 2-Week follow-up calls to customers to ensure their satisfaction and up-sell additional products and services<br>
<br>
-Calling through existing customer database to identify additional sales opportunities and soliciting new business<br>
<br>
-Continuously build upon your knowledge of wireless products and services through formal Verizon training, as well as independent research<br>
<br>
-Handle all customer service issues in a timely and professional manner<br>
<br>
-Maintain store appearance by cleaning fixtures, updating promotional materials &amp; price cards and restocking merchandise<br>
<br>
We are looking for a motivated self starter who wants to take a good job and make it into a thriving career.  We offer a competitive salary (based on experience) + commissions.  If you think you're right for the position then don't hesitate.  We are looking to hire IMMEDIATELY, but only the right candidate.  Please send your resume for consideration.  If you have what it takes, we will call you shortly for an interview.  Thank you for your interest.  <br>
<br>
    </section>

